rComments: Best professor at uOttawa. He regularly updates his material so it stays relevant and interesting. I was anything but bored, sometimes a little 'keep Summer safe' mind blown. Unlike the many courses I've taken here that we have to take for the sake of taking them, because of reasons. I actually retained pertinent information that matters
Excellent Prof! Matière claire et très interessante!
Great prof!!! Very interesting and clear! :)
Best prof I've had! He makes sure you understand the material. Made microbio very easy!
No textbook required. Just attend class and focus on the material he emphasizes. A lot of slides, many of which were unnecessary but interesting course and relatively easy for a science course.
